#DATA TYPES challenge
#find the sum of first and second digit of a given two digit number

#request a two digit number and store it
#remember that input will convert to string
num = input("Type a two digit number: ");

#create a variable to hold first digit || typecast the first char of num
i = int(num[0])
#create a varible that holds the second digit || typecast the second char of num
j = int(num[1])

#print out the sum
print("The sum is ", i + j)
